flowchart TD
    A[open /dev/... ] --> B[spec_open in specfs]
    B --> C{v_type}
    C -->|VCHR| D[cdevsw major d_open]
    C -->|VBLK| E[bdevsw major d_open]
    D --> F[driver open routine]
    E --> F
    F --> G{device number changed?}
    G -->|yes| H[makespecvp newdev replace vnode]
    G -->|no| I[return vnode]
